snippet.title: Phantasy Star Online 2 - Sonic Collaboration Edition
snippet.description:
Phantasy Star Online 2, one of Japan's biggest online RPGs is finally coming to North America! Play on Xbox One for free now!

★  Become a founder by purchasing the Sonic Collaboration Edition!
For more information, visit: https://pso2.com/news/announcements/founderspack

★ PSO2 Social
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PSO2Official
